bilingual.target: 整个过程花了九周时间。

bilingual.source: Repeat the process with brightly coloured tissues.
bilingual.target: 用鲜艳的纸巾重复这个过程。

bilingual.source: The process also produces more greenhouse gases.
bilingual.target: 这个过程还会产生更多的温室气体。

bilingual.source: To me, the process is even more important than the dinner itself.
bilingual.target: 对我来说，过程比晚餐本身更重要。

bilingual.source: The samovar tea-making process is quite special and has two stages.
bilingual.target: 茶炊的制茶过程非常特别，有两个阶段。

bilingual.source: Research the process you are going to describe, writing down some key facts.
bilingual.target: 研究你要描述的过程，写下一些关键事实。

bilingual.source: An explanatory text explains a process or tells us how something works.
bilingual.target: 说明文解释一个过程或告诉我们某物如何运作。
你可以反转这个过程吗？

bilingual.source: Use spc to monitor the quality of the production process.
bilingual.target: 使用统计过程控制来监控生产过程的质量。

list.abstract: process（英[ˈprəʊses，prəˈses]，美[ˈprɑːses，prəˈses]），英语单词，作名词为步骤；程序；方法。作动词为对…进行加工；列队行进；处理。短语搭配有in the process of（在…的过程中）。例句为“It slows down our aging process.（它减缓了我们的衰老过程。）” process动词类近义词有manufacture、cope with等。process现在分词形式是 processing。
《Process》是Sampha的首张个人录音室专辑，由Sampha担任制作人，共收录10首歌曲，于2017年2月3日发行。 2017年，该专辑获得第26届英国水星音乐奖年度专辑。

yingyinNormal.en: In the book, she describes a selection process.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她在书里描述了一种挑选过程。

yingyinNormal.en: In some sense it's a self-fulfilling process.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在某些意义上这是个令人有满足感的过程。

yingyinNormal.en: I know the process is frustrating, but it's so worth it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道过程是让人沮丧的，不过是值得的。

yingyinNormal.en: From this point in the process, gravity takes the grain through the mill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个过程中重力作用 粮食就进入磨里。

yingyinNormal.en: What's your next move? One option is a process called permineralization.
yingyinNormal.zh: 下一步干吗呢？一种选择是经历所谓的石化过程。

yingyinNormal.en: It's just part of the process. Such setbacks will test you. They sort people.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这都是过程。这种挫折会考验你。分出不同人群。

yingyinNormal.en: Probably. But will you accept? No. But I shall enjoy the process enormously.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可能吧，你会接受吗？不，但我会非常享受那个过程的。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, It depends. On? On how far along he is in the sexchange process.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗯, 那要看情况。什么情况？看他是在变性过程中的什么阶段啰。

yingyinNormal.en: The last step in this long process, an intrepid paleontologist has to come find you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个漫长过程的最后一步，一位勇敢的古生物学家必须要找到你。

yingyinNormal.en: By doing that over and over again, I learned to love this process, even the crashing part of it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一遍又一遍，我学会了热爱这个过程，热爱跌倒的体验。

yingyinNormal.en: Photosynthesis is an intricate process that science is still trying to unlock.
yingyinNormal.zh: 光合作用的过程十分错综复杂，科学家们还在不断尝试着解开它的奥秘。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, Joey has a very careful screening process. Apparently, not everyone is qualified to own wood and nails.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔伊有一套严格的筛选过程，并非每个人都适合拥有木制品。

yingyinNormal.en: Plus a roundtable on the nonequilibrium green's function approach to the photoionization process in atoms.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有用非平衡格林函数解决原子内光化电离过程的圆桌会议呢。

yingyinNormal.en: This process requires a lot of cushion space between the point she starts falling and the ground.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个过程要求在她开始下落的地点到地面之间有一个很大的缓冲空间。

yingyinNormal.en: That process also creates a high energy molecule, called ATP which the cell uses to power all of its parts.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个过程同时制造出一个高能量分子，叫做三磷酸腺苷，为细胞供给能量所用。

yingyinNormal.en: The process is highly volatile. If one isn't protected by a specialized helmet, it can affect the brain's chemistry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他的研究过程很不稳定，如果没有专业头盔的保护，将会影响大脑化学反应。

yingyinNormal.en: Check this out. Look at that. Wow, that's amazing. The crystallization is an exothermic process, so the ice is actually hot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看好了。我看看。这好厉害啊。它的结晶是一种放热过程，所以这个冰是热的。

yingyinNormal.en: That much is suggested by the economy of choice, acquainted with the process of death, but unsentimental about the necessity of disposal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 经济的选择表明了这点，她熟悉死亡的过程，但是对于身后事并不在意。

yingyinNormal.en: But, if you took advantage of modern marketing techniques, and you optimized your manufacturing process, you might be able to make this a viable business.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是，如果你利用现代营销技巧优化生产过程，或者能做好这门生意。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, that's right. And, so far, each of your fellow defendants has specifically denied being part of that process. Now, I'm going to ask you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，没错。到现在为止，其他几位被告都否认自己曾参与这一过程。现在，我要问你。

examination_example.sentence: It uses analytics to help identify where there may be bias in the hiring <highlight>process</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它使用分析来帮助识别招聘过程中可能存在偏见的地方。

examination_example.sentence: But demanding too much of air travelers or providing too little security in return undermines public support for the <highlight>process</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 可是，如果对飞机乘客的要求过于苛刻，或者相应的安全保障太少，反过来就不利于民众对安检进程的支持。

examination_example.sentence: But too often we take this <highlight>process</highlight> too far and end up suppressing emotions, especially negative ones.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但我们往往把这个过程看得太远，最终会导致压抑的情绪，尤其是负面情绪。

sense_info_list.en: a method of producing goods in a factory by treating natural substances
sense_info_list.zh: 工序; 处理; 加工

examination_example.sentence: People made car-buying decisions only if the decision was complex—when they had a lot of information to <highlight>process</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 人们只有在决策复杂的情况下——当他们有大量信息需要处理的时候，才会做出购车决定。

examination_example.sentence: Under existing law NHS "controlled" the data and DeepMind merely "<highlight>processed</highlight>" it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 根据现行法律，NHS 信托“控制”了数据，而DeepMind只是“处理”了数据。

examination_example.sentence: Passengers must pay $85 every five years to <highlight>process</highlight> their background checks.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 乘客必须每五年支付85美元来处理他们的背景调查。

sense_info_list.en: a series of actions or steps taken in order to achieve a particular end

examination_example.sentence: Hiring professionals to navigate the whole <highlight>process</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 雇佣专业人士来指导整个过程。

examination_example.sentence: Getting input from others not only offers a fresh perspective and thought <highlight>process</highlight>, it often also includes riskier choices.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从别人那里获得投入不仅提供了一个新的视角和思考过程，它往往还包括更多的风险选择。

examination_example.sentence: The state's facilities management project team is still in the <highlight>process</highlight> of developing its business justification.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该州的设施管理项目小组仍在制定其业务依据。

sense_info_list.en: a method of producing goods in a factory by treating natural substances

examination_example.sentence: Everything from production to storage and <highlight>processing</highlight> must improve.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从生产到储存和加工的一切都必须改进。

examination_example.sentence: It allows more information to be <highlight>processed</highlight> quickly.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它允许更多的信息被快速处理。

examination_example.sentence: Computer can <highlight>process</highlight> what it sees--then recognize a face it's told to find--with remarkable speed and precision.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 计算机能够以惊人的速度和精准性处理所看到的东西，从而识别出要找的脸孔。

sense_info_list.en: a series of changes that happen naturally

examination_example.sentence: Many public health policymakers believe that the resolution of age-associated disease will tell us something fundamental about the ageing <highlight>process</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 公共卫生政策制定者认为，年龄相关疾病的解决将能告诉我们老龄化过程的一些基本情况。

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>process</highlight> of ageing can ultimately be brought under control.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 衰老的过程最终得以控制。

examination_example.sentence: We can postpone the eventual stop of cells' dividing through nutrition, exercise, good sleep and even relaxation techniques, but we cannot stop the ageing <highlight>process</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们可以通过营养、锻炼、良好的睡眠甚至放松技巧来推迟细胞分裂的最终停止，但我们无法阻止衰老过程。

examination_example.sentence: These are <highlight>processes</highlight> that you are developing so that you are able, over time, to tackle more interesting problems, more challenging problems — problems that require many people instead of one person, and many skills instead of one.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这种实践都是你逐渐展开的过程，久而久之你就能够处理更有趣以及更具挑战性的问题——这是问题需要多人合力，而非某个人的一己之力来解决。

examination_example.sentence: And involving the future residents in the <highlight>process</highlight> can be very important.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 让未来的居民参与到这个过程中是非常重要的。

examination_example.sentence: It's pointless unless there is a repeatable <highlight>process</highlight> in place to turn inspiration into financial performance.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 除非有一个可重复的过程，可以将灵感转化为财务业绩，否则这是毫无意义的。

sense_info_list.en: a method of producing goods in a factory by treating natural substances

examination_example.sentence: Every day, USPS <highlight>processes</highlight>, on average, 493.4 million pikes of mail-anything from postcards to Social Security checks to medicine.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国邮政总局每天平均处理4.934亿封邮件——从明信片到社会保障支票再到药品。

examination_example.sentence: Mail that was already <highlight>processed</highlight> in New Orleans facilities was moved to an upper floor so it would be protected from water damage.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 已经在新奥尔良处理过的邮件被转移到了高楼层，这样邮件就不会因为沾水而造成损坏。

examination_example.sentence: Grenade says sugar and <highlight>processed</highlight> foods are big contributors to the rising diabetes rates among children.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 格雷纳德说，糖和加工食品是导致儿童糖尿病发病率上升的重要原因。

examination_example.sentence: The salt, sugar, fat and <highlight>processed</highlight> foods in the American diet contribute to the nation's high rates of obesity, diabetes and heart disease.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国人饮食中的盐、糖、脂肪和加工食品导致了美国肥胖症、糖尿病和心脏病的高发率。

examination_example.sentence: Slowing down their ageing <highlight>process</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 减缓他们的衰老过程。

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>process</highlight> is tiring.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 过程很累。

examination_example.sentence: If others benefit in the <highlight>process</highlight>, and I get some reward too, does it really matter where my motivation lies?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果别人在这个过程中受益，而我也得到了一些奖励，那我的动机是什么真的重要吗？

examination_example.sentence: It starts with understanding who you are with respect to the natural world and how you approach the gardening <highlight>process</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它始于明白就自然界而言你是谁，以及如何处理园艺工作流程。

sense_info_list.en: a method of producing goods in a factory by treating natural substances

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Processes</highlight> the natural language it hears
examination_example.sentence_trans: 处理它听到的自然语言

examination_example.sentence: We will also discuss the origins of felt (毛毡), what enables wool fibres to become felt and how the <highlight>processes</highlight> we use work.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们还将讨论毛毡的起源，用什么把使羊毛纤维变成毛毡，以及我们使用的工艺是怎样的。

examination_example.sentence: On every single move you have to analyze a situation, <highlight>process</highlight> what your opponent (对手) is doing and evaluate the best move.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在每一步行动中，你都必须分析形势，考虑对手的行动，评估出最佳的一步。

examination_example.sentence: In the <highlight>process</highlight>, the tea loses nearly all of its healthy parts.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在这个过程中，茶叶几乎失去了所有健康的部分。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 在这个过程中，人类仍然决定正确的答案。

examination_example.sentence: Hosting it is a <highlight>process</highlight> of learning about poetry and performing,” said Dong.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 董说：主持它是一个学习诗歌和表演的过程，”。

examination_example.sentence: They <highlight>process</highlight> (加工) more than 92 million tons of water every day.

examination_example.sentence: Our minds <highlight>process</highlight> a lot of information and time seems to slow down.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们的大脑处理大量信息，时间似乎变慢了。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 这将增加我们大脑处理的信息量，扩大我们对时间的体验。
